query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.favorite_count >= 0 AND q.favorite_count <= 10000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('android-6.0-marshmallow',
'android-webview',
'assemblies',
'code-coverage',
'crystal-reports',
'hover',
'mathematical-optimization',
'open-source',
'passport.js',
'powershell-2.0',
'refresh',
'string-formatting',
'xna');
